---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout category="company">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">사업소개</h1>
    <div
      class="max-w-6xl w-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-8 p-10"
    >
      <!-- Main Circle - Shareholder's Meeting -->
      <div
        class="flex-shrink-0
        rounded-full w-60 h-60 bg-primary
        flex items-center justify-center
        text-white text-center shadow-lg relative"
      >
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">주주총회</h2>
          <ul class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li>의결권 모집</li>
            <li>주주총회 시나리오</li>
            <li>주총장 경호 및 보안</li>
            <li>주주총회 전반 업무</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Connected Right Sections -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 w-full">
        <!-- Asset Operation -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 shadow-md"
          >
            <img
              src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/000000/settings.png"
              alt="icon"
              class="w-8 h-8 opacity-70"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">자산 운영</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              국내 및 해외자본유치 / 프로젝트 관리 및 추진 / 신규 프로젝트 발굴
              / 리서치, 정보관리 / 특화된 투자전략
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Structure Adjustment -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 shadow-md"
          >
            <img
              src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/000000/graph-report.png"
              alt="icon"
              class="w-8 h-8 opacity-70"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">구조 조정</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              기업가치평가, 투자분석 / M&A 자문 / 워크아웃, 회사정리, 회의절차
              대행 / 자산관리, 투자업체 Restructuring
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Management Consulting -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div
            class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 shadow-md"
          >
            <img
              src="https://img.icons8.com/ios/50/000000/briefcase.png"
              alt="icon"
              class="w-8 h-8 opacity-70"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">
              경영 컨설팅
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              NPL 평가, ABS 발행 자문 / 매매전략 자문 및 중개 / 자산실사 /
              국내상장관련 업무·자문, 벤처 컨설팅
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
